text.tspan: Political civil liberties weighted by population, World, 1800 to 2022
Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem. It captures the extent to which people enjoy the freedoms of
expression and association. The variables ranges from 0 to 1 (most liberties).
Source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
